Class Project

java.lang.Object
Entity.Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a public housing project managed by the HDB. Contains information about the project's name, location, unit types, availability, timeline, and assigned officers.

      public Project(String name, String neighbourhood, List<FlatType> flatTypes, LocalDate openingDate, LocalDate closingDate, HDBManager manager, int officerSlots, List<HDBOfficer> officers)
      Constructs a new Project instance with the provided parameters.
      Parameters:
      name - the project name
      neighbourhood - the location of the project
      flatTypes - list of flat types and their details
      openingDate - the opening date of the project
      closingDate - the closing date of the project
      manager - the HDB manager in charge
      officerSlots - number of officer slots available
      officers - list of officers assigned to the project
